{"tid":2020241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬌認凍卵求子　賀爾蒙失調爆肥9公斤","createTime":"2020-05-17T02:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T02:37:32.000Z","uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c534663a3d657427faa59f5c671099d0034c2403","tid":2020241,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:09:33.000Z","msg":"阿嬌先前就曾傳出為了保持卵子健康，早就凍卵，就等婚後開始做人計畫，阿嬌今也坦承已經凍了3顆卵子，原本醫生勸她多做幾次，不過她因為凍卵造成賀爾蒙失調，爆肥20磅（約９公斤）減不下來，讓她直呼過程比健身還辛苦，不會再考慮凍卵了。（吳佩蓁／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20181204/UHUH4HMAFTQPWY2KXYSNFPPT7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20181204%2FUHUH4HMAFTQPWY2KXYSNFPPT7E%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e612hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=b5920258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20181204%2FUHUH4HMAFTQPWY2KXYSNFPPT7E%2F&h=d07fc746\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20181204/UHUH4HMAFTQPWY2KXYSNFPPT7E/</a>"},{"pid":"724f50486d018cb8bfb6ab70d9af574aef553239","tid":2020241,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LD7fP6r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLD7fP6r.jpg&h=915c0334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e931a85c7de0de35efeda66e7ba66d90f23fb747","tid":2020241,"uid":198362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"吸精大法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HivdBVo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHivdBVo.gif&h=7e5c9039&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}